  "texts": [
    "In the above experiments, we have revealed that the temporal features with different timescales can be integrated by multiple dendritic branches within DH-LIF neurons.",
    "In this subsection, we try to demonstrate another route for integrating multi-timescale temporal features through synaptic connections.",
    "Here synaptic connections include feedforward connections between layers in SFNNs and recurrent connections within layers in SRNNs.",
    "To support our prediction, we test the one-layer DH-SFNN, the two-layer DH-SFNN, and the one-layer DH-SRNN, all of which only have one dendritic branch in each DH-LIF neuron to eliminate the influence of intra-neuron feature integration.",
    "The task is the same multitimescale spiking XOR problem as above and the network structures can be found in Supplementary Fig."
